  "intent_precise": "3.1 & 3.2 Incubation Recovery & Pre-Amplification PCR: Using dummy_plate (labware, slot DUMMY PLATE), pre_amp_rack (labware, slot PREAMP RACK), RECOVERY AGENT RACK (labware, slot 3), SAMPLE PLATE (labware, slot 1). With magnetic module, temperature module, temperature module. (1) Set temperature to 4\u00b0C. (2) Mix 1 times at 130\u00b5L. (3) Wait 3 seconds. (4) Incubate for 2 minutes. (5) Pause: \n    Ensure the solution developed into a biphasic mixture, then select\n    \"Resume\" in the app.\n     (6) Pause: Proceed directly to Pre-Amplification PCR.\n                 No cleanup step is required. (7) Transfer 35\u00b5L from source to destination.",
